The Scaperune teleport is an item from the 2019 Christmas event, given to the player by Santa in order to leave ScapeRune after convincing Anti-Santa to help him deal with his son, Jack Frost.

Despite what the name and examine text implies, the tablet is actually used to teleport to the bakery.
